/ available locals are
/ grid   : the fancygrid instance
/ cell   : the column to render
/ record : the datarecord for the current row to render
/ value  : the value for current cell to render

/ example rendering the actions show and edit for a users table
- case grid.name
- when :companies
  - case cell.name
  - when :actions
    = link_to "Show", company_path(record)
    = link_to "Edit", edit_company_path(record)
    
    
- when :roles
  - case cell.name
  - when :actions
    = link_to 'Show', record
    = link_to 'Edit', edit_role_path(record)
    = link_to 'Destroy', record, :confirm => 'Are you sure?', :method => :delete